1.content:
Maron guild is one of the largest mercenary guilds of Gilderock. They are taking any kinds of orders, be it protection or monster hunting. Most of guild members are forming groups within it. Ranking:
Vice-master - Phoneim;
Officers - Ambisha, Shruti, Senritsu, Kagura, Ramiela;
Lieutenants - Harmony, Tonika, Kanon, Musa, Luciera, Jade;
Soldiers - Bamil, Rhythmi, Symphoni, Simone, Arco, Repolis, Rosemary, Cecilia, Sonaria, Miriam, Adriana, Teria, Taisa, Hariel, Deka, Greythroat, Vollet;
Newbies - Almis, Mina, Breath, Fiona, Rafina, Lericys, Klara, Inga.

44.content:
Gangs in Gilderock have a large influence on life in the city. You  can't make a move without them knowing it.
List of Gangs:
Big three - Erune family, the Avengers, Ireto Trade;
Bone Watchers;
Slana's Hands.

